S13_MAINTAINER_REFERENCE - 维护者速查表

[Description]
高频文件、符号和行号索引。

[UML]
None

[Detail]
| 区域 | 符号/文件 | 位置 |
| --- | --- | --- |
| SDK public API | `deepagents.__all__` | `libs/deepagents/deepagents/__init__.py:26-48` |
| SDK state | `DeepAgentState` | `libs/deepagents/deepagents/graph.py:63-66` |
| SDK main entry | `create_deep_agent` | `libs/deepagents/deepagents/graph.py:217-829` |
| SDK default prompt | `BASE_AGENT_PROMPT` | `libs/deepagents/deepagents/graph.py:69-142` |
| SDK required middleware | `_REQUIRED_MIDDLEWARE` | `libs/deepagents/deepagents/graph.py:187-201` |
| SDK final graph | `create_agent(...).with_config(...)` | `libs/deepagents/deepagents/graph.py:806-829` |
| CLI parser | `_build_parser` | `libs/cli/deepagents_cli/main.py:82-115` |
| CLI dispatch | `cli_main` | `libs/cli/deepagents_cli/main.py:131-173` |
| Deploy command | `execute_deploy_command` | `libs/cli/deepagents_cli/deploy/commands.py:129-217` |
| Deploy project model | `Project`, `Skill`, `Subagent` | `libs/cli/deepagents_cli/deploy/project.py:115-157` |
| Deploy project load | `Project.load` | `libs/cli/deepagents_cli/deploy/project.py:159-188` |
| Deploy payload | `build_payload` | `libs/cli/deepagents_cli/deploy/payload.py:20-43` |
| Deploy directory delta | `build_directory_delta` | `libs/cli/deepagents_cli/deploy/payload.py:86-98` |
| ACP bridge | `AgentServerACP` | `libs/acp/deepagents_acp/server.py:92-206` |
| Code CLI app | `DeepAgentsApp` related Textual app code | `libs/code/deepagents_code/app.py` |
